Sentencas: The Pb2Ru2-xBixO7 (x = 0, 0.2, and 0.4) pyrochlore oxides have been studied as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Characterization of Pb2Ru2-xBixO7 (x=0, 0.2, and 0.4) pyrochlore oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All the samples synthesized by co-precipitation method were single phase pyrochlore oxides.
Titulo: Characterization of Pb2Ru2-xBixO7 (x=0, 0.2, and 0.4) pyrochlore oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Pb2Ru2O7 shows high electrical conductivity of over 2 x 10(3) S.cm(-1).
Titulo: Characterization of Pb2Ru2-xBixO7 (x=0, 0.2, and 0.4) pyrochlore oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Both electrical conductivity and thermal expansion coefficient decrease with an increase in the Bi content.
Titulo: Characterization of Pb2Ru2-xBixO7 (x=0, 0.2, and 0.4) pyrochlore oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Pb2Ru1.8Bi0.2O7 showed the lowest polarization resistance of 0.12 Omega.cm(2) at 800 degrees C in an air atmosphere.
Titulo: Characterization of Pb2Ru2-xBixO7 (x=0, 0.2, and 0.4) pyrochlore oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
